7.What images are used in the new webapp pod?
You must look at all the pod's containers in detail to figure this out.

Run the command kubectl describe pod webapp and look at the images used.

8.What is the state of the container agentx in the pod webapp?
Wait for it to finish the ContainerCreating state

Run the command kubectl describe pod webapp and look at the state of the agentx container.

9.Why do you think the container agentx in pod webapp is in error?
Inspect the events of the pod to determine the reason for the container's failure to start.

Run the command kubectl describe pod webapp and look under the events section.
